profile:
AM Group of Companies has been in operation since 1956 and is a 3rd generation family business.

We stand behind our work with one of the best warranties in the business, 10 years. This is only possible as a result of three things: the use of premium products, good workmanship and careful inspection of completed work.

AM Group of Companies hires only skilled workers who are regularly educated on installation methods and new materials. Our corporate education programs apply to all facets of the business.

Proudly situated in Guelph, London, Owen Sound, Gravenhurst and Collingwood, our size and office geography allow us to deliver corporate-grade professionalism while maintaining top rate local customer service.

AM Group of Companies Services:
Commercial Roofing
Residential Roofing
Fiberglass Shingles, Metal Roof, Flat Roof, Cedar Shakes & Shingles, Composite Roofing, Inspire, Owens Corning, Enviroshake.
Eavestrough, Soffit, Fascia and other Aluminum work
Attic Insulation, Blown In Insulation
Skylights, Velux
Ventilation
Roof repair & replacement
Siding
Windows & Doors
Vinyl Windows
Entry Doors
Patio Doors
 
Contact us today for a Free, no obligation estimate.
1-877-281-6900

profile:
​​​​​MJ Guardian Roofing Ltd started off as a small locally owned business here in the GTA. Over the years, we expanded to Barrie, Kitchener and Niagara Falls Areas. The exceptional quality of our workmanship as well as our top customer service have made us one of the biggest and most noted company to service southern central Ontario.

​Our dedication to the craft has generated us a large client base in both residential and commercial roofing. What differentiates us from our competitors is the experience of our workers in the field, our competitive pricing, our flexible scheduling, as well as our commitment to our work.

We currently offer a wide array of roofing related services, including shingle replacements, flat roofs, metal roofs, eaves trough repair and replacements, soffits and fascia, rooftop solar system installation, skylight repair and installation, and attic spray foam insulation. We also cater to new constructions and townhouse co-ops. We prioritize the safety of both our workers as well as you and your family, and are fully insured and licensed. We also offer warranty for all our services.

Call our number today for all your roofing inquiries!​​

profile:
Jim’s Roofing and Renovations Inc. is a family-owned and operated company located in Guelph. Our company has been serving the GTA and Hamilton area, as well as surrounding areas for over 30 years. Our installers specialize in all types of roofing applications - full installations as well as  repairs  with shingles, cedar, flat roofs, skylights, vinyl and aluminum siding as well as full trough installation. 

Our installers are up to date with the latest roofing technology to offer you the best products available. We are experienced in a variety of sloped roof applications such as Asphalt Shingles, Cedar Shake, Enviroshake and Slate Tiles. We also install a variety of skylights and sun tunnels. We are experienced in a variety of flat roof applications such as TPO, EDPM, Mod Bit, 4-Ply and Dec-Tec. We also have experienced installers for copper work, metal pans, eavestrough, fascia/soffit, as well as aluminum/vinyl siding and specialty siding such as Hardie Board, Maibec and cedar siding. Our service scope includes residential, townhouse complexes, condos, commercial buildings and industrial locations. All of our installers are certified in Working at Heights and follow all safety protocols to ensure a clean/safe work environment for everyone.  

For many years, Jim's Roofing and Renovations has had a successful partnership with numerous restoration and insurance companies.  Our role is to provide emergency services to home owners when unexpected damages occur as a result of wind and ice storms, fire and tree damage. 

From the initial contact for a free detailed no obligation estimate to the final steps of the installation and every aspect in between, Jims Roofing and Renovations strives towards working with you as the Homeowner to collaboratively meet your roofing and renovations needs and expectations.   Quality workmanship is a standard in our company and we stand by our written labour warranty and provide a manufacturer warranty for our clients.  

Working At Heights and Safety protocols are followed on all job sites.  Jim's Roofing and Renovations is fully covered under WSIB and carry Commercial Liability Insurance.  

We would like the opportunity to provide you with a free no obligation estimate for your roofing and renovation projects.

profile:
Welcome to Irvine Roofing and Siding and our "Online Showroom"
. . . Kenneth Irvine - Your Personal Roofing & Remodeling Advisor

Our website is designed to explain your choices of products and services available for your roofing or home remodeling project.

Please review the various areas to help you make an informed decision and to build confidence we are the right contractor for your roofing project.

We'll make sure your home makes a striking impression, adding the greatest curb appeal in your neighborhood. Attention to detail, quality products and quality craftsmanship is key.

Your choice of roofing material is an important decision when protecting your home from the elements, bringing out the beauty and extending the useful service life of your roof system.

Anyone has the ability to drive a nail through a shingle, but if that was all there was to proper shingle installation, we would not be replacing roofs installed by others that are failing only a couple of years later!

Homeowners have numerous choices of products, styles and design options. There are several shingle and shingle type materials . . . Asphalt, Wood, Tile, Metal, Composite and more . . .

Choosing the right contractor to install your roof is just as important as selecting quality materials.

With so many products available, we'll help you make "Your Best and Safest Choice."

We are a "full service" roofing company and we will handle everything from a new roof installation, restoration and maintenance to re-roofs and repairs. All with the assurance that can solely come with years of experience.

Quality craftsmanship and design are key - and we go beyond the basics with innovative maintenance programs, extended warranties and great customer service, ensuring our customers' satisfaction and their roof's long term performance.

Please check us out here:

We have provided top-quality roofing services to the area for many years, accumulating a list of hundreds of satisfied customers along the way. 

We’re proud of our reputation for quality, dependable roofing services and work hard to ensure complete satisfaction on each and every job we undertake. 

Whether you need simple repairs before the next rainy season or a whole new roof, give us a call today and let our experience go to work for you as your roofing contractor in your area.

profile:
At Mitchel's Roofing and Renovating we bring the best material and labour at a cost that is lower than competition. Having no overhead keeps our costs lower than bigger competitors, so that we can sustain profit and with that a small incline of sales. Cost of production may stay the same, while operations costs fluctuate from customer to customer will always maintain profit margins. Since Employee Training, Equipment Maintenance, and New Equipment Purchases go into productivity our objective is to satisfy customers by providing all the resources our employees need to remain as productive as possible, even 10% finders fee on flyers, most sales in a month, employee birthday parties, and employee of the Month bonuses.
Excellent Customer Service helps us to retain clients like our Customer Appreciation Day, Questionaires and follow -ups, flyers program and the Renovating will generate repeat revenue. Keeping our customers happy is our primary objective, at Mitchels Roofing and Renovating. By offering our other  programs such as snow removal, yard cleanup and other small jobs, we can still keep customers happy while keeping our objective in place.  Employee turnover may cost us money in lost production and costs assocciated with recruiting which includes employment advertising and paying placement agencies.
At Mitchels Roofing and Renovating we maintain a productive and a positive employee environment and improves retention. By having birthday parties, flyers program, employee of the month and even sales person of the month and with team meetings once a week to get feedback and questions or something new to add by suggestions.

Mitchels Roofing and Renovatings' core values become our objective necessary to create a positive culture between customers and employees. Since our growth is based on historical data and future productions such as going above and beyond our competition and ongoing services. Since our growth requires the careful use of business resources such as finance and personal which is 36 yrs personally making customers happy along side with employees.
specialities:
Our Mission
​

At Mitchels Roofing and Renovating our mission is to satisfy customers one by one, by taking the utmost pride in workmanship while still keeping staff motivated. We believe in giving customers the proper satisfaction they deserve and want. Having customers wanting our services and when finished then telling others, friends, family, and neighbors. By taking pride from the time the flyer is passed on or info till the time we complete the task at hand to clean-up and container removed from property. Workmanship and pride will show customers that we at Mitchels Roofing and Renovating like in the past, customers are so  happy that they boast about us and our services and our ongoing support care.
